@startuml Operator_Sequence
title Operator Module - Order Processing Workflow

actor Operator as O
participant OperatorDashboard as Dashboard
participant Backend
participant Database
participant DocumentService
participant SupplierService
participant NotificationService

O -> Dashboard: Open operator dashboard
Dashboard -> Backend: tRPC operator.getQueue(filters)

Backend -> Database: Query fizbo_orders + document statuses
Database --> Backend: Return active orders sorted by urgency
Backend --> Dashboard: Return queue with real-time updates

Dashboard -> O: Display order list [Status | Days Open | Urgency]
O -> Dashboard: Click order to view details

Dashboard -> Backend: tRPC operator.getOrder(orderId)
Backend -> Database: Query FizboOrder + Property + Documents
Database --> Backend: Return complete order context

Dashboard -> O: Display order detail panel

== Document Status Update ==
O -> Dashboard: Update document status: Missing → Requested
Dashboard -> Backend: tRPC operator.updateDocumentStatus(docId, "requested")

Backend -> Database: Update fizbo_documents.status = "requested"
Database --> Backend: Confirmation

Backend -> DocumentService: Mark document as requested
DocumentService -> NotificationService: Send DOCUMENT_REQUESTED notification

NotificationService --> O: System log: "Notification sent to seller"

alt Requires Supplier Coordination
  O -> Dashboard: Select "Coordinate with Perito"
  Dashboard -> Backend: tRPC operator.requestSupplier(orderId, "perito")
  
  Backend -> SupplierService: Get available peritos (municipality)
  SupplierService --> Backend: Return perito list with pricing
  Backend --> Dashboard: Show perito selection dropdown
  
  O -> Dashboard: Select perito + preferred date
  Dashboard -> Backend: tRPC operator.bookSupplier(perito_id, date)
  
  Backend -> SupplierService: Send booking request (WhatsApp/email)
  SupplierService --> Backend: Booking confirmation
  
  Backend -> Database: Create supplier assignment record
  Backend -> NotificationService: Send SUPPLIER_BOOKED notification
  NotificationService --> O: Confirm booking logged
end

== Seller Action Required ==
alt Order Needs Seller Input
  O -> Dashboard: Click "Request Seller Action"
  Dashboard -> Frontend: Show action type selector
  
  O -> Dashboard: Select "Provide procuration" + compose message
  Dashboard -> Backend: tRPC operator.requestSellerAction(orderId, "procuration", message)
  
  Backend -> Database: Create seller action request
  Backend -> NotificationService: Send SELLER_ACTION_REQUIRED notification
  NotificationService --> Seller: Email + WhatsApp with instructions
  NotificationService --> O: Confirmation
end

== Blocked Order ==
alt Order is Blocked
  O -> Dashboard: Flag "Bloqueada"
  Dashboard -> Backend: tRPC operator.flagBlocked(orderId, reason, est_resolution_date)
  
  Backend -> Database: Update fizbo_orders.status = "blocked"
  Backend -> Database: Store reason + estimated resolution
  
  Backend -> NotificationService: Send ORDER_BLOCKED notification
  NotificationService --> Seller: Email + WhatsApp: "Your order needs attention: [reason]"
  NotificationService --> O: Order flagged in queue
end

== Mark Complete ==
O -> Dashboard: Verify all docs complete
O -> Dashboard: Click "Mark Order Complete"
Dashboard -> Backend: tRPC operator.completeOrder(orderId)

Backend -> Database: Update fizbo_orders.status = "complete"
Backend -> Database: Set completed_at = now()

Backend -> NotificationService: Send ORDER_COMPLETE notification
NotificationService --> Seller: Email + WhatsApp: "All documents ready"

Backend -> Inngest: Trigger docready/order.complete event
Inngest -> Backend: Queue SmartCMA generation (async)

Dashboard -> O: Confirmation: "Order complete. SmartCMA queued."

note right of Backend
  Real-time updates via
  Supabase Realtime
  No manual refresh
end note

@enduml
